APP INFORMATION: PRIVACY POLICY
Introduction
Thank you for using our Doc Scanner App (“the App”). We are committed to protecting your privacy and providing a safe and secure user experience. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle information within our app and explains your rights related to privacy and data protection.
Information We Do Not Collect
We are proud to inform you that our App does
not
collect any personal information or data from its users. We do not require you to sign up, log in, or provide any personal details such as your name, email address, phone number, or any other personally identifiable information (PII).
Data Usage and Storage
No Data Collection
: Our App does not collect, transmit, or store any data related to your scanned documents or usage patterns. All scans and related data remain solely on your device and are not uploaded to any external servers.
No Third-Party Access
: We do not use any third-party analytics or tracking tools within the App. Your activity is completely private, and there is no access or sharing with third-party services.
Permissions
To function correctly, the App may request access to certain features of your device, such as the camera and storage. These permissions are used solely to provide the scanning functionality and to save your scanned documents locally on your device. The App does not use these permissions for any other purposes.
Security
We are committed to ensuring that your data remains secure. Since no data is collected, stored, or transmitted outside your device, there is no risk of unauthorized access or misuse by the App itself.
Children’s Privacy
Our App is intended for use by individuals of all ages. However, as it does not collect any personal information, it complies with regulations regarding the privacy of children online.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When changes are made, the updated policy will be made available within the App. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your privacy.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us at:
LAUMOBILESCANNER@GMAIL.COM
Conclusion
Your privacy is our top priority, and we have designed this App with your security and privacy in mind. We hope this clear and straightforward policy gives you confidence in using our Doc Scanner App.
Thank you for trusting us!